</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="118v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l9">Chuncʒen von herbolcʒheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l11"> <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft beuor . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als das hans </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l10">Cuncʒ </ab></add> von herbolcʒheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l12">Als du vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haſt / von Jacob Toplers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l13">vnd der Schenkſtat vnd erbs wegen cʒu Argerſheim / 
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l15">vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . vnd alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir darümb den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l17"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> cʒurede geſacʒt . des antvvurtt . vnd dein brief 
<add><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l16">den du vns geſant haſt </ab></add> niht v̈berain </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l18">lawten . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvie darümb / deuht dich daʒ du darümb cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l19">dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> heſt / darümb <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l20">vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough">dich </del> dır oder deinem <expan>ſcheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l21">
<add>von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan></add> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſleunigs <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir des ermant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l22">werden . ſo derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> ıſt / deuht dich <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l23">daʒ du cʒu der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Schenkſtat oder dem erb 
<del rend="strikethrough">dauon </del> icht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l25"> <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> heteſt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſo </del> darümb maht tu die 
<add><ab facs="#facs_237_line_1571837504057_747">vvol </ab></add> fürvvenden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l26">in <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> lant </del><expan>geriht<ex>en</ex></expan> / da die hingerhört / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l27"><expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="118v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Chunczen von Herbolczheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft bevor. <add>Cuncz</add> von
                        Herbolczheim, als du uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast von Jacob
                        Toplers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und der schenkstat und erbs wegen czu
                        Argersheim, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>. Und also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir darümb den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> czu rede gesaczt, des antwurtt und dein
                        brief, <add>den du uns gesant hast</add>, niht überain lawten.
                                <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wie darümb deuht dich, daz du darümb
                        czu dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> iht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        hest, darümb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir oder deinem
                                <expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <add>von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> sleunigs
                            <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                        ermant werden, so derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> ist; deuht dich <expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan>
                        daz du czu der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> schenkstat oder dem erb
                        icht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hetest, darümb maht tu die
                            <add>wol</add> fürwenden in <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geriht<ex>en,</ex></expan> da die hingerhört.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
